1166
00:50:07,180 --> 00:50:09,100
They're doing fast of
anywhere from 12 to 16 hours,

1167
00:50:09,100 --> 00:50:12,150
every 24 hour cycle, that's
actually what my practice is.

1168
00:50:12,150 --> 00:50:13,760
I do that on a regular
basis, sometimes the,

1169
00:50:13,760 --> 00:50:15,335
I eat breakfast,

1170
00:50:15,335 --> 00:50:16,890
but normally I pushed breakfast
out to about 11 or noon,

1171
00:50:16,890 --> 00:50:18,100
or sometimes a little later,

1172
00:50:18,100 --> 00:50:19,800
some people are doing longer fast,

1173
00:50:20,905 --> 00:50:21,738
