and inflammatory markers.

1543
01:06:56,710 --> 01:06:58,460
And this is a beautiful
study because it was done

1544
01:06:58,460 --> 01:07:00,710
in hundreds of human patients.

1545
01:07:00,710 --> 01:07:02,510
These actually weren't
patients that were sick,

1546
01:07:02,510 --> 01:07:06,320
I should say human subjects
that were otherwise healthy

1547
01:07:06,320 --> 01:07:09,180
from a huge variety of
backgrounds, so you had men,

1548
01:07:09,180 --> 01:07:10,960
you had women, you had people

1549
01:07:10,960 --> 01:07:13,220
of different races, different ethnicities.

