non-digestible are only partially

1555
01:07:25,670 --> 01:07:27,960
digestible carbohydrates typically.

1556
01:07:27,960 --> 01:07:29,660
And they compared that to diets

1557
01:07:29,660 --> 01:07:33,420
that were unchanged, except
for the inclusion of a few,

1558
01:07:33,420 --> 01:07:36,680
to a few more servings of
fermented foods, each day,

1559
01:07:36,680 --> 01:07:39,010
things like sauerkraut,
things like kimchi,

1560
01:07:39,010 --> 01:07:41,000
they even explored, it
sounds pretty disgusting

1561
01:07:41,000 --> 01:07:42,230
to me, but who knows, I've never tried it,

1562
01:07:42,230 --> 01:07:44,680
which is fermented cottage cheese.

