01:07:44,680 --> 01:07:47,460
And what they found was
that after initial period

1564
01:07:47,460 --> 01:07:50,370
of a few weeks, where they
had people either eat a lot

1565
01:07:51,310 --> 01:07:54,700
of fiber or eat one or two
servings of fermented foods,

1566
01:07:54,700 --> 01:07:57,530
they had those people ramp
up their ingestion of either

1567
01:07:57,530 --> 01:08:00,200
fiber or fermented foods, so
they kind of ease them into it.

1568
01:08:00,200 --> 01:08:01,950
As they went baseline then ramp up

1569
01:08:01,950 --> 01:08:04,400
to the point where they
were ingesting, you know,

1570
01:08:05,427 --> 01:08:06,690
four or five servings of fiber or

1571
01:08:07,817 --> 01:08:10,420
of fermented foods per day,
which sounds like a lot.

