01:08:27,640 --> 01:08:30,890
And they did this by fecal
samples, by stool samples,

1581
01:08:30,890 --> 01:08:33,020
and they did this by blood
draw, which is great,

1582
01:08:33,020 --> 01:08:34,410
it's a real power of this study.

1583
01:08:34,410 --> 01:08:37,620
In fact, the most comprehensive
study that I'm aware of.

1584
01:08:37,620 --> 01:08:40,450
By looking at these different
tissues across long periods

1585
01:08:40,450 --> 01:08:44,990
of time, so many weeks, and
