1586
01:08:44,990 --> 01:08:47,410
to the diet that they were
on before they went into the

1587
01:08:47,410 --> 01:08:51,430
study, they will were able
to establish in a causal way,

1588
01:08:51,430 --> 01:08:55,729
how ingesting fibers or fibrous
foods versus ingesting these

1589
01:08:55,729 --> 01:08:58,369
fermented foods on a daily
